---
title: Pan-Fried Double Salmon and Bok Choy with Spicy Mayo and Ginger Jasmine Rice
description: For tonight's speedy Japanese-inspired feast, salmon is pan-fried to a crispy finish, while bok choy gets a sweet teriyaki glaze. Ginger-infused rice makes a hearty, aromatic base, and there's even creamy sriracha mayo to drizzle over everything!
